                        <h1>
                            Acts and regulations</h1>
                    
                
            </div>
        </div>
    

<div class="documentBody" id="Tekstinnhold">
    
    
    
        <div>
            

<div>
	<p>Government.no does not publish a complete overview of valid acts and regulations. For a complete overview (in Norwegian), <a href="http://www.lovdata.no" target="_blank"><font color="#0000ff">check Lovdata</font></a>, which, in addition to the overview, also publishes all&nbsp;acts and regulations in their entirety.</p>
